User Stories

User Story #1: As a roommate, I want to view a shared dashboard so that I can see all assigned chores, deadlines, and completion statuses in one place.
User Story #2: As a roommate, I want to mark chores as completed so that progress is visible.
User Story #3: As an admin, I want to manage shared expenses so that rent payments remain organized and controlled.

